{
  "chapter": 35,
  "chapter_summary": "温黛黛在少林寺苦候云铮二十日，云铮却已由无色大师送往常春岛。温黛黛绝望欲寻死，被黑衣女子试探后跳崖，加入常春岛黑袍组织。铁中棠偶遇温黛黛，得知常春岛之事。铁中棠在酒铺发现沈杏白以常春岛为饵诱骗云铮，遂跟踪至海边大船。冷一枫已出家为道士，练就毒功，与司徒笑、黑星天、白星武、盛大娘母子聚会，追讨被盗万两黄金。盛存孝挺身担责。司徒笑透露五福连盟有司徒知人公遗书记载退敌之计，暗示五家胜大旗门非靠武功而是靠阴谋。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_se_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "无色大师",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你来了么，好好，且坐下来，听贫僧说几句话。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_se_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "无色大师",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你必知道他已走了，乃是老衲送他走的。为了一件十分重大之事，他也不得不走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_wu_se_da_shi",
      "text": "他……他为何不对我说一说？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_se_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "无色大师",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "他走时老衲也曾问他，可要见你一面，他也曾考虑许久，却终于决定还是不见的好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_wu_se_da_shi",
      "text": "他……他为何如此忍心？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_se_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "无色大师",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "无情便是有情，唉……有情不如无情。只是万物众生，俱都有情，是以众生苦恼。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_wu_se_da_shi",
      "text": "大师慈悲，告诉我他到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_se_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "五色大师",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "常春岛。老衲说了，你也不会知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_wu_se_da_shi",
      "text": "常春岛在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_se_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "五色大师",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "老衲也不知，只是要他自己寻去，但以他性情，只怕不到地头，半途便会……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_se_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "五色大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何处是地头，何处不是地头，咄，老衲又着相了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_wu_se_da_shi",
      "text": "大师要他去常春岛，为了何事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_se_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "五色大师",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "有因必有果，有果必有因，有今日之果，必为昔日之因，他去得自有道理……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣女子",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你真的要死么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "不错，我要死了，你待怎样？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣女子",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你年纪轻轻，口里说要去寻死，只怕不过是一时冲动，过一会儿又不想死了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "这人生有何意思，我为何还想活着？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣女子",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "如此说来，你想必是伤透了心啦！莫非是你所爱的人对不起你，将你抛下了不管？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "也不用你来管！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣女子",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你……你到底要怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣女子",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "我也是个伤心人，我也想死，你既决心想死，不如和我一起去死吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "好，想不到我黄泉路上，还有同伴……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣女子",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "随我来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣女子",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "到了，就是这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣女子",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你还等什么？快跳下去吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好一个寻死之处……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣女子",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你若不愿死，回去还来得及。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我为何回去？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍妇人",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你可受惊了？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "我已决心求死，你们为何还要如此戏弄我这苦命的人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍妇人",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "正因你是个苦命的人，我们才要如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍妇人",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "因为我们也都是苦命的人，所以要收容天下苦命的女子。但若非决心求死，还算不得真正命苦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "所以你们便要试试我，是么？但你们……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍妇人",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "我们都已死过了一次，所以要你也死一次，才能加入我们这一群中。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_yi_hei_pao_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "另一黑袍女子",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "此刻你我都是已死的人，再过几天，你就会知道做死人的滋味比活人好得多。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不愿做死人……不愿做死人……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍妇人",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你已死过一次，还想活么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你……你们究竟是谁？为……为何要我加入你们？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍妇人",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "做了死人，便可做上天的使者，便可为天下受苦受难的女子抱不平，你难道还不愿意么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "难怪她们行事说话那般冷漠，原来她们人虽未死，心却早都死了……后来呢？你可曾……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "我的心也死了，我自然加入她们。自此我也身着黑袍，面蒙黑纱。我心里虽有许多疑问，但她们却不许我问她们任何话，只说：我的心既已死了，还管那么多事作甚？还问什么？我只得跟着她们走，路上只要看到女子受了欺侮，她们必定出手相救，直走到这里。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你可知道她们此刻要去哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "回去……若不是车子里有两个奇怪的病人，我们早已回去了，只怕……只怕也永远再见不着你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你们回去的地方，也正是我要去的地方，只是……我若非遇见你，却不知路途走法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你怎知我们要回到哪里去？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "此事说来话长，但我却知你们要回常春岛。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你莫非还不知常春岛这名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "她们只说回家，始终未说家在何处。我有时甚至以为那是在天上，或是在地下。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "无论如何，你总……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "她们已在催我回去了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "我跟着去可使得？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "好吧！但我们要在前面一间圣母祠中歇至四更才会启程，到时你再来吧，只是行藏须得十分小心，若是被她们发觉，就不好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "你到底知不知道常春岛在什么地方？可要老实说，这不是好玩的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "小弟若不知道，怎敢来骗大哥。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "唉，你这人的确不错，想不到你我萍水相逢，你竟待我如此，而我自己弟兄，却是个人面兽心的恶徒。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "大哥，你怎的又提到那姓铁的了？那种恶徒、淫贼，提起来岂非败了你酒兴。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，来，我自罚一杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "其实这常春岛究竟该如何走法，小弟也知道得并不十分清楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "你……你莫非故意戏弄于我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "大哥莫要着急，小弟虽不清楚，却可将大哥平平安安，送上常春岛。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "如何送法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "大哥今日只管放心喝酒，到了明日，去到海边，小弟寻得几个经常往来常春岛的船户，只要借一帆顺风，后日清晨，便可安抵常春岛了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "好兄弟，再干一杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "这件事你办得很好，一点都未着痕迹。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "你暗中弃了黑星天，投靠老夫，足见你目光明确，选择得当。此事若是成了，老夫必不致亏待了你。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "多仗老爷子栽培。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "今日之江湖，高手屡出，似黑星天那样的武功，已只能跑跑龙套，哪里能成大事？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "老爷子说的是，不但他们不成，就连风九幽，又怎能比得上你老人家神功绝世？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "小孩子不要乱拍马屁。嘿嘿，只要你老实卖力，老夫何尝不能将那神功传授于你。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "晚辈只要能学着你老人家一成武功，就已心满意足了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "好，好，好，你连日辛苦，此刻不妨歇歇，明天好打起精神做事。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "是，多谢你老人家。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "沈杏白，你在这里守住姓云的小子，切切不可疏忽。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "你老人家只管放心就是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "等我走后，你再拍开他的穴道，将他稳住。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "他醉得糊里糊涂，怎会知道被人点过穴道？弟子只要三言两语，包管将他制得服服贴贴。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "好，你留意我烟花火号，只要烟花一起，你便带着姓云的赶去，不起烟花，不得下车走动。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "冷一枫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 437,
      "line_end": 437
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "各位果然守信，准时在此相候于我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "小弟接得冷兄相约之柬，怎敢有误？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "冷兄远来，先用些酒菜点点心腹，再说正事也不迟！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "我近来已不食人间烟火，自家带得有下酒物，不劳你费心。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_xing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "黑星天",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "不知冷兄带的是什么仙家下酒物？小弟可有这份口福也分一杯尝么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_hei_xing_tian",
      "text": "自然有的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_hei_xing_tian",
      "text": "这便是我的下酒物，黑兄既要分一杯羹，就请莫要客气，只管用吧，请……请……",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_xing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "黑星天",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "小……小弟无福消受，冷兄只……只管自用吧！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，我就不客气了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，美味……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "我已用过了点心，咱们不妨谈谈正事了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然自然……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "不知那蛇头可吃得么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "text": "蛇头是否吃得，白兄现在总知道了吧！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "知……知道了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_xing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "黑星天",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "不……不知冷……冷兄的竹篓里，还……还有什么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_hei_xing_tian",
      "text": "怎么？黑兄又想分一杯羹了么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_xing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "黑星天",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "不是不是……小弟只是问问。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，问问就问问。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "各位打算拖到什么时候，才肯让我说到正事？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "小弟们根本不知道冷兄要说的究竟是什么事，怎会有故意拖延时间之心？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "真不知道？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "小弟怎敢相欺……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "我冷一枫走南闯北数十年，大小身经数百战，却不想今日竟有人将我当做呆子。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "冷兄未免言重了，小弟们对冷兄一向尊敬有加，冷兄怎能如此说话？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "不如此说话，却该怎样说话？寒枫堡窖藏的万两黄金，莫非不是你们盗去的么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么黄金？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_hei_xing_tian",
      "text": "黑兄、白兄、盛大娘，你们可曾瞧见冷兄的黄金？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "有群不开眼的贼子，乘我不在堡中，偷去了堡中万两黄金，我只当是各位所为……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "冷兄必定是误会了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "若不是各位，却是谁呢？莫非是那些不孝不义，禽兽不如，见不得人的无耻小贼不成？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_cun_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "盛存孝",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "不用骂了，那黄金是我盛存孝取来用了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_dai_niang",
      "speaker_name": "盛大娘",
      "listener": "char_sheng_cun_xiao",
      "text": "孝儿，你……你疯了么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_sheng_cun_xiao",
      "text": "到底是盛存孝敢作敢为，但却未免太呆了，明明是别人主谋，却偏要扯到自己头上。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_cun_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "盛存孝",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "全是我一人所为，自应一人担当。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_sheng_cun_xiao",
      "text": "真是你一人盗的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_cun_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "盛存孝",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_sheng_cun_xiao",
      "text": "既是如此，老夫少不得要教训教训你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_dai_niang",
      "speaker_name": "盛大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慢来！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_sheng_dai_niang",
      "text": "怎样？莫非还有你一份么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_dai_niang",
      "speaker_name": "盛大娘",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "司徒笑、黑星天、白星武，你们眼见我儿子挺身而出，还好意思坐在那里么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来你们也不愧是男子汉。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "咱们未经允许，便取了冷兄黄金，只因咱们知道，若是说出理由，冷兄一定会答应的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_xing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "黑星天",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "咱们心想冷兄反正是会答应的，先拿后拿岂非一样？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "是以咱们就先拿了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "呵呵，可笑啊可笑，想不到三位对老夫的心思，倒比老夫自己还要了解！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "是什么理由？且说来听听。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "数十年来，大旗门虽屡次向我五家寻仇，但屡次都是大败而返，这原因为了什么，冷兄可知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "自是咱们武功高强，将他们打败了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 646
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "冷兄取笑了，其实冷兄必也知道，咱们五家的武功，实比不上大旗门的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "这话也不错，尤其是咱们五家，多的是贪生怕死之徒，怎比得上人家那种剽悍勇敢之气。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "弱能胜强，这原因小弟本也不知，直至此次大旗门重出之后，小弟遵先父遗命，开拆了他老人家一封遗书，才知道其中究竟……说到此点，冷兄必然要奇怪，为何五福连盟，只有我司徒家有遗书叙述其中原因，别人家却没有……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "不错，老夫正在奇怪。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "今日我五家虽惟冷兄马首是瞻，但昔日的五福连盟，却是由先父知人公主盟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "你说得太客气了，各位什么事都将我冷一枫蒙在鼓里，这便是惟我马首是瞻么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "昔日五福连盟一切退敌之行动，大多由先父知人公策划，是以事后自由先父留下遗书，而先父这封书，却命小弟要等到大旗重来后方能开拆，里面便说的是如何退敌之计。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_xing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "黑星天",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "司徒前辈行事之周密小心，当真非常人能及，他老人家生怕别人知道此中的隐秘，是以只由他一人留下遗书，又定要大旗重来之日才能开拆，这一切为的只是避免事机不密，泄漏出去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "咱们的退敌之计，为何要如此保守隐秘，难道这些妙计都是见不得人的么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "不瞒冷兄说，你我五家先人的退敌之计，委实有些见不得人的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 682
    }
  ],
